{"tid":1383850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"物資組都要升級","createTime":"2019-07-29T19:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:12:44.000Z","uid":103534,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2dcd5a64d54ff6fd502015eef6abf8c07f0380","tid":1383850,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有見突然有大量市民捐物資，物資物必需好好發揮功用</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先要為物資分類，意思係將高級豬咀留起俾前線嘅勇士。<br />\n<br />\n建議如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.成立物資應變小隊，遊走前線，睇下邊個唔夠裝，幫佢加裝或者換裝。主動去幫前線好過，因為實際對戰時，物資站同前線都有段距離，加上前線根本冇時間去後場攞資源。另外一個問題就係有批勇士好多時留力，通常下半場先入，高級物資好多時都冇左。加上一到場已經9衝去前線，根本冇時間去搵物資站。<br />\n成立流動補給小隊，可以幫手解決多條戰線手足唔夠裝嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n2.教育很重要，要長期抗爭，物資唔可能無限供應。所以有人攞物資要講明，早走嘅唔好掉物資，可回收或者下次用。如果唔識處理，佢都可以裝啲裝pass俾前線嘅朋友，總好過掉左佢。<br />\n<br />\n3.幫手睇下有冇年輕手足有冇生活上需要幫助，我地都明好多後生仔因為呢個幾月已經乾溏，守望相助。佢地真係未必會講出聲，但我地多口問多兩句真係會幫到佢地手。我相信，佢地對落場嘅手足信任度都會高啲。<br />\n<br />\n其他有冇人補充？</span><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 199"},{"pid":"1effac43202d4c32d01e58a8da0dfd774506688d","tid":1383850,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:17:29.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a7be5f70cfb852746f929a698565381627767","tid":1383850,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"推到物資組睇到。。。可能已經訓晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9527107cac46ac2c53bb3c466b505321a7eab545","tid":1383850,"uid":164496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:19:40.000Z","msg":"非常清晰既整合<br />\n建議每個方向都開一個tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f208baa8e6f23101dc31c161478b7bb835e7f14","tid":1383850,"uid":268725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:20:36.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69usdxa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69usdxa.png&h=afc4f3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求 拒絕警黑勾結<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"9a8c096194b6a17b79637b8ed353d31761cb57c6","tid":1383850,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:31:49.000Z","msg":"1號我已經同朋友準備做"},{"pid":"f104a97f148c6f89dcd424102c41d857a7a8a34d","tid":1383850,"uid":99442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"[國外採購]<br />\n<br />\n想問如果帶物資俾大家, 最需要既野, 依次序係?<br />\n- 頭盔<br />\n- 濾罐/罩<br />\n- 口罩<br />\n- 眼罩<br />\n<br />\n有埋型號preference更佳.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4969d0619f86a92c0afc81ee83e2cf05fb2a4983","tid":1383850,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"893bc28ec974a178a72371f375d458fe2fd09b48","tid":1383850,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人加油！<br />\n堅持我地既信念<br />\n只做岩既事<br />\nDo the right things </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"15b27175ac66ea9bb100c859c073e6e0cd30c992","tid":1383850,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e48dc2fb5e31e07c8cdaf2ab70efdd34209053c0","tid":1383850,"uid":164496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f104a97f148c6f89dcd424102c41d857a7a8a34d","tid":1383850,"uid":99442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"[國外採購]<br />\n<br />\n想問如果帶物資俾大家, 最需要既野, 依次序係?<br 